This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection in images and videos. The use of depth information also suggests that it could belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could place it in the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the potential use of the proposed method in unmanned aerial vehicles and drones suggests that it could also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
